<item>
 <title>Kerala Boat Song</title>
 <link>https://vse.la/vidya-vox/kerala-boat-song</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;I&#039;ve come so far&lt;br /&gt;
From where I&#039;ve began&lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s the sound of the waves&lt;br /&gt;
The breeze on my skin&lt;br /&gt;
Wish that&lt;br /&gt;
I could be back&lt;br /&gt;
Back in my homeland singing&lt;br /&gt;
Thi thi thara thi thi thai&lt;br /&gt;
Thi thai thaka thai thai thom&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Show me the road&lt;br /&gt;
And I&#039;ll be right there&lt;br /&gt;
I&#039;ll do, anything to feel&lt;br /&gt;
The wind in my hair&lt;br /&gt;
I&#039;ll go, far as it takes&lt;br /&gt;
And I won&#039;t even care&lt;br /&gt;
I&#039;ll sing thi thi thara thi thi thai&lt;br /&gt;
Thi thai thaka thai thai thom&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Kuttanadan punchayile, thi thai thaka thei thei thom&lt;br /&gt;
Kochupenne kuyilale, thi ti thara thei thei&lt;br /&gt;
Kottuvenam kuzhal venam, kurava venam&lt;br /&gt;
Kottuvenam kuzhal venam, kurava venam&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ooh...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thi thi thara thi thi thai&lt;br /&gt;
