[x8]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&#039;s been ten years&lt;br /&gt;
But I spent each day thinking&lt;br /&gt;
What if I hadn&#039;t gone&lt;br /&gt;
What if I&#039;d stayed but when&lt;br /&gt;
So many waves are calling me away&lt;br /&gt;
I&#039;ll sing thi thi thara thi thi thai&lt;br /&gt;
