&lt;p&gt;It fills my heart like no other song can&lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s the sound of the race&lt;br /&gt;
The boats leave the land, take me&lt;br /&gt;
Back to the waters of my homeland&lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;ll sing thi thi thara thi thi thai&lt;br /&gt;
Thi thai thaka thei thei thom&lt;/p&gt;

