<item>
 <title>New Horizon</title>
 <link>https://vse.la/matt-darey/new-horizon</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;It&#039;s been a long time&lt;br /&gt;
Since our ships set sail&lt;br /&gt;
All along a muddy river&lt;br /&gt;
Until we reached out for the sea.&lt;br /&gt;
We were crossing miles and miles.&lt;br /&gt;
We were sailing nameless fields.&lt;br /&gt;
Once we lost our guiding star.&lt;br /&gt;
A roaring ocean took us far away.&lt;br /&gt;
Away, away, away, away,&lt;br /&gt;
Away, away, away, away,&lt;br /&gt;
Away, away, away, away,&lt;br /&gt;
Away, away, away, away.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Far away..&lt;br /&gt;
From here.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Far away...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Far away.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Far away from here.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[Chorus]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
A heart of mine come lead me the way,&lt;br /&gt;
A heart of mine me won&#039;t go astray,&lt;br /&gt;
Come lead me to a new horizon,&lt;br /&gt;
Where are my doubts are flown away!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Where we walking for the line.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&#039;s been a long turn,&lt;br /&gt;
And we are driving on and on,&lt;br /&gt;
Floating through these waves&lt;br /&gt;
In search of love and freedom.&lt;br /&gt;
Or tell me we can make it through a storm,&lt;br /&gt;
Sail around the swords of evil.&lt;br /&gt;
The flamings skies shall open up now&lt;br /&gt;
Open up.&lt;br /&gt;
And carry us to land&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Us to land&lt;br /&gt;
Us to land&lt;br /&gt;
Re. Us to land&lt;br /&gt;
Us to land&lt;br /&gt;
Us to land&lt;br /&gt;
Us to land.&lt;br /&gt;
Re. Us to land&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(Chorus)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;What was that we were looking for?&lt;br /&gt;
What is that we are looking for?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The way!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Way!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
